data.description: This Craftsman-style home is nestled in a charming and secluded neighborhood and exhibits a thoughtfully designed floor plan, attention to detail, and beautiful sunset views! The versatile bonus room could easily be utilized as a 4th bedroom, and the vaulted living room with wood beams creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. Your family will enjoy the spacious yard and the conveniences of town while being surrounded by the serenity of farmlands. Don't miss out on your opportunity to make this house your new HOME!
